All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Affector
    Affector fields, that apply forces to SmoothMovers inside them.
    Ball
    Ball, affected by gravity and collisions.
    BlackHole
    A Black Hole, sucks in the ball and ends the game.
    Collider
    Parent class for all objects that need to collide with each other in a rigid body physics system.
    Cursor
    Cursor, follows mouse, and handles drawing the LaunchArrow and launching the Ball.
    Flag
    Flag, end goal of a level.
    LaunchArrow
    Line drawn from the Cursor to the Ball, to illustrate to the player that they're hitting the ball.
    Planet
    Planet, collides with the Ball and has an affector to pull the Ball.
    SmoothMover
    A variation of an actor that maintains precise location (using doubles for the co-ordinates instead of ints).
    Space
    Space, area for space golf to take place.
    Spike
    Spike hazard, sits on a planet and ends the game if touched by the ball.
    Vector
    A 2D vector.
